docs.title: Introduction
docs.description: Webex Meeting Center today has three distinct meeting experiences: Personal Meeting Room (PMR), Scheduled Meetings, and Space Meetings. Each of these meeting types has distinct experiences, USM is to consolidate the experiences of Space Meetings with Scheduled Meetings and meld together the experiences. Get the single meetings experience in Webex App.
